{"tid":354931,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"京都一日遊疑問","createTime":"2017-08-11T01:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T03:12:59.000Z","uid":18444,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e1aedca0c3c4766dedab183c0c904e77558e2fe","tid":354931,"uid":18444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:23:45.000Z","msg":"九月同老公會兩個人去5日4大阪<br />\n其中1日會plan去京都1日<br />\n行程：伏見稻荷》二条城》錦市場》<br />\n           花見小路》清水寺<br />\n<br />\n如果想夜晚7點起行番大阪<br />\n呢d景點行唔街得哂？<br />\n<br />\n另外我見到伏見稻荷、二条城、花見小路<br />\n都各有一間出名既鰻魚飯<br />\n請問邊間會好食d？<br />\n定還是去番廣川<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後問多樣就係有無係呢個路線上<br />\n有比較經濟既懷石料理？（午餐）<br />\n<br />\n唔該各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6327463aaac120cfac7144d3ba942f68c158341f","tid":354931,"uid":18444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:36:24.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 唔記得講8點半係大阪出應該10點到稻荷<br />\n同埋係唔使著和服既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb9c4ba113bf1e3e9a528aeca8b2e89411ee2d2","tid":354931,"uid":18444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:39:02.000Z","msg":"仲有應該唔會食廣川啦 原來係嵐山 <br />\n唔打算去果邊了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de861a58bc00d65b4ebcae15cbe2b8fda30f782e","tid":354931,"uid":49797,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:50:29.000Z","msg":"9個鐘去5個點<br />\n你想每個點影張相打個卡就走咪ok<br />\n但咁chur為乜<br />\n咪咁貪心啦"},{"pid":"34dace0cf54713a9cf3afff22bff7fc99a0f5332","tid":354931,"uid":58250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:57:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>9個鐘去5個點<br />\n你想每個點影張相打個卡就走咪ok<br />\n但咁chur為乜<br />\n咪咁貪心啦</blockquote><br />\n我都係咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係一個二条城都睇半日啦<br />\n我朝早10點幾到睇完都4點幾5點"},{"pid":"2f82478ff2befb8f754a4452ae4bcefc664b68af","tid":354931,"uid":35363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:01:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>九月同老公會兩個人去5日4大阪<br />\n其中1日會plan去京都1日<br />\n行程：伏見稻荷》二条城》錦市場》<br />\n           花見小路》清水寺<br />\n<br />\n如果想夜晚7點起行番大阪<br />\n呢d景點行唔街得哂？<br />\n<br />\n另外我見到伏見稻荷、二条城、花見小路<br />\n都各有一間出名既鰻魚飯<br />\n請問邊間會好食d？<br />\n定還是去番廣川<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後問多樣就係有無係呢個路線上<br />\n有比較經濟既懷石料理？（午餐）<br />\n<br />\n唔該各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個行程似跑馬多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為伏見行下睇下都冇左兩個鐘<br />\n同埋你要預景點之間嘅搭車時間<br />\n仲有 夜晚繁忙時間好撚多人<br />\n我等左5班車(15分鐘一班巴士)都未上到車番到京都站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23998f6d2056e3c6fb8ba12cde00eaad5aa8173a","tid":354931,"uid":49797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:02:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>九月同老公會兩個人去5日4大阪<br />\n其中1日會plan去京都1日<br />\n行程：伏見稻荷》二条城》錦市場》<br />\n           花見小路》清水寺<br />\n<br />\n如果想夜晚7點起行番大阪<br />\n呢d景點行唔街得哂？<br />\n<br />\n另外我見到伏見稻荷、二条城、花見小路<br />\n都各有一間出名既鰻魚飯<br />\n請問邊間會好食d？<br />\n定還是去番廣川<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後問多樣就係有無係呢個路線上<br />\n有比較經濟既懷石料理？（午餐）<br />\n<br />\n唔該各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個行程似跑馬多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為伏見行下睇下都冇左兩個鐘<br />\n同埋你要預景點之間嘅搭車時間<br />\n仲有 夜晚繁忙時間好撚多人<br />\n我等左5班車(15分鐘一班巴士)都未上到車番到京都站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n租隻馬去行都死"},{"pid":"497ed20c195c6130924b0dab10bdc4a04ff311a3","tid":354931,"uid":18444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:24:30.000Z","msg":"如果cut二条城會唔會輕鬆d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d004bbad9429bb3845344e85eef51c16189c8ed2","tid":354931,"uid":49797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:26:32.000Z","msg":"不如你略略講下其他日子會行幾多野"},{"pid":"35e32d2efb75c04422d892ad224d316e86c61bae","tid":354931,"uid":123825,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:32:40.000Z","msg":"二条城都唔去嘅話 去京都把撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95cc9a9b06ed0be702f01edc193ce0c1b64c11bc","tid":354931,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:34:38.000Z","msg":"大阪兩日咩都夠啦<br />\n<br />\n其他時間留係京都仲好"},{"pid":"e7417e2264432a93ab6baf82f3030e8d865606fa","tid":354931,"uid":18444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:36:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如你略略講下其他日子會行幾多野</blockquote><br />\n其他都係大阪..."},{"pid":"c11c5ec27a6b4ef9ca8a2d22b05f6972b4c7ab51","tid":354931,"uid":130834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:37:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>二条城都唔去嘅話 去京都把撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解一定要去二条城<br />\n你咁講佢京都去得一日<br />\n好多個景點都去唔到<br />\n全部都可以話 &quot;XXX都唔去既話去黎把撚&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e6ccdaf6f532bb54f059de44d2abca7fa25cf46","tid":354931,"uid":18444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:37:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>二条城都唔去嘅話 去京都把撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實主要係想去伏見稻荷大社<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26f761e9f08485365e13f41d53f4648f42575db4","tid":354931,"uid":42426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:41:21.000Z","msg":"巴打識玩<br />\n包架車每個地方落車影張相打個卡都有D趕"},{"pid":"87e462fbd8b3bd47021ea83efdbfe6634a60297a","tid":354931,"uid":130834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:42:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好意思 唔記得講8點半係大阪出應該10點到稻荷<br />\n同埋係唔使著和服既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你行程咁趕仲咁遲先到稻荷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早啲出門口吧啦"},{"pid":"5d90ed51ddc7cb079af548ceef4ff73f16dc130b","tid":354931,"uid":18444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:42:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打識玩<br />\n包架車每個地方落車影張相打個卡都有D趕</blockquote><br />\n我唔多影相的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只不過今次係淺度遊 <br />\n等下次先行多d野"},{"pid":"1d6e677ad0568c37d53b4c6bbf2ae3190b4db09b","tid":354931,"uid":18444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:44:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔好意思 唔記得講8點半係大阪出應該10點到稻荷<br />\n同埋係唔使著和服既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你行程咁趕仲咁遲先到稻荷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早啲出門口吧啦</blockquote><br />\n去旅行唔想咁早去身呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前係東京都係訓到十二點幾起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"262f3219c75a07c64f33ed8ec72c3ef580934388","tid":354931,"uid":130834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:46:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔好意思 唔記得講8點半係大阪出應該10點到稻荷<br />\n同埋係唔使著和服既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你行程咁趕仲咁遲先到稻荷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早啲出門口吧啦</blockquote><br />\n去旅行唔想咁早去身呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前係東京都係訓到十二點幾起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁就咪plan到咁撚趕啦<br />\n你如其每度都望2眼好似無去過咁<br />\n下次又要再花時間去睇真啲<br />\n不過集中啲睇2-3個位好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318dc03a8bf7a76d6b723965ad3833bac4b5247b","tid":354931,"uid":18444,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:47:50.000Z","msg":"行程：伏見稻荷大社》錦市場》花見小路》清水寺<br />\n<br />\n咁樣應該應該10am-7pm應該玩得哂？"},{"pid":"2bd3e6b890a862102688b032186e8f73d963b9ca","tid":354931,"uid":35363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:52:31.000Z","msg":"樓豬 清水寺大修喎 真係仲去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n京都一日遊 伏見 錦市場 再加多個景點就好走<br />\n順帶一提 京都啲巴士就好似香港嘅 53 / 64K 咁慢 到時樓豬上唔到巴士唔好嗌救命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5f07aa76584b225e8132ba874ede98192abf83","tid":354931,"uid":98431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:58:51.000Z","msg":"打卡式行程 你跟旅遊書去算啦"},{"pid":"74729052780776e1a6db29740a69f6527556a701","tid":354931,"uid":18444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T03:08:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬 清水寺大修喎 真係仲去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n京都一日遊 伏見 錦市場 再加多個景點就好走<br />\n順帶一提 京都啲巴士就好似香港嘅 53 / 64K 咁慢 到時樓豬上唔到巴士唔好嗌救命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去清水寺都係諗住行二年坂 三年坂 <br />\n真係寺入面既話都無咩大期望<br />\n一黎知道裝修二黎唔係賞楓既季節"},{"pid":"f4933c334dbefca4695f48e7ae51b6abc5e0bfb6","tid":354931,"uid":18444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T03:10:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打卡式行程 你跟旅遊書去算啦</blockquote><br />\n所以咪問下夠唔夠時間行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左旅遊書我都上網睇左人地行程先問<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有做功課嫁"},{"pid":"788c669692154b56c80c1eaf6233138ab51586c6","tid":354931,"uid":135118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T03:15:17.000Z","msg":"伏見稻荷係行山咁行<br />\n兩粒鐘都未必行得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}